cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for video representation using image compression and adversarial training. This approach is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) as it involves image analysis techniques for video analysis. The use of adversarial training also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper evaluates the proposed method for activity recognition, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
